{"tid":2220144,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣六都遭「市長聯盟」標示為中國　首長齊抗議！不排除退出","createTime":"2020-09-27T12:03:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T21:14:59.000Z","uid":115579,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"39dfb6c4bf27d1c95fa93e22dfae89fb350beb5f","tid":2220144,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T12:03:46.000Z","msg":"聯合國真係正一垃圾組織<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n國際組織「市長聯盟」官方網頁竟台灣加入聯盟的6都城市國籍都標示為「中國」，對此六都首長均表示不滿。高雄市長陳其邁嚴正表示，拒絕矮化、已要求正名，「台灣從來就不是中國的一部分，我們有名、有姓」<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n「市長聯盟」是聯合國城市氣候高峰會於2014年9月所成立，目的是串聯全球各城市，以最大的努力對抗氣候變遷的挑戰，由C40城市氣候變遷領導小組、地方政府永續發展理事會（ICLEI）和城市與地方政府聯盟（UCLG）等三大城市網合作組成。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20200927/ZSXKAGANKFCINOCR3OH5A6UI5Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20200927%2FZSXKAGANKFCINOCR3OH5A6UI5Q%2F&d=4SaXJ4tauImRU00LhBBHUvG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=8ae8b771\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20200927%2FZSXKAGANKFCINOCR3OH5A6UI5Q%2F&h=dc4de2c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20200927/ZSXKAGANKFCINOCR3OH5A6UI5Q/</a>"},{"pid":"c1856d188ba11ad4ccecce14fde4c7481c23f9d4","tid":2220144,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T12:37:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1493baf66351543a63549d8fc242ed3c97b58fc","tid":2220144,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T21:14:59.000Z","msg":"推"}]}